I would like to see the hawks  grouping and raiding more as a guild, but I also would like to see us  being more prepared  for hunts and raids.<br>
Here are a few items that are a must for all players over the lvl of 50 to carry  with them for raids, and or hunts..<br>
<br>
1. Stack of  food<br>
2. Stack of water<br>
3. Stack of batwings ( for those times we all need lev)<br>
4. Stack of fishscales ( for the enduring breath)<br>
5. Thurgadin gate potion ( for non gating classes, this is a must... come on hawks work up the pottery skills.. can easily be done in  approx 2hrs of game)<br>
6. Pearls ( for times when cothing is used.. each time a mage casts this, it is one pearl .. average price 5pp)<br>
7. Peridots ( melee classes wishing to have an ac/hp buff ... all the cleric buffs at this lvl, require a peridot per cast .. average price 10 pp) [ It is not uncommon for a cleric to go thru a stack or more , per night, on a raid]<br>
 And of course for them wonderful nights... when the raid gets jolly.. a coffin in the bank.<br>
     If we all show up to a raid on time and prepared, the hunts are much smoother, and will be more enjoyable for all..<br>
                                  Xoel..<br>
